Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra

Class GF2mMatrix

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.Matrix
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.GF2mMatrix
public class GF2mMatrix extends Matrix
This class describes some operations with matrices over finite field GF(2m) with small m (1< m <32).
See Also:
Matrix
